---
alwaysApply: true
---

---
description: Figma-based UI alignment rules
globs:
  - "app/**/*.tsx"
  - "components/**/*.tsx"
  - "src/**/*.tsx"
---

When working on UI, design, layout, or frontend visual refinement:

- Use the Figma MCP server first.
- Treat Figma as the source of truth for visual design.
- Treat the codebase as the source of truth for functionality.
- Do not remove code-only functional UI additions just because they are not present in Figma.
- Visually adapt code-only elements to match the active design language.
- Preserve responsiveness, dark mode, light mode, sidebar/topbar behavior, and component consistency.
- Refactor existing pages/components instead of regenerating entire screens whenever possible.
